people don't know is

00:15:37.630 --> 00:15:40.210 align:middle line:10%
that when you have an
emotional reaction,

00:15:40.210 --> 00:15:42.060 align:middle line:10%
there's a refractory
period of chemicals

00:15:42.060 --> 00:15:45.000 align:middle line:10%
