00:16:00.059 --> 00:16:01.100 align:middle line:90%
So what's wrong with you?

00:16:01.100 --> 00:16:02.377 align:middle line:90%
Well, I'm in a mood.

00:16:02.377 --> 00:16:03.460 align:middle line:90%
Oh, why are you in a mood?

00:16:03.460 --> 00:16:06.530 align:middle line:84%
