in the brain and the body

00:16:49.650 --> 00:16:50.970 align:middle line:90%
as if the event was happening.

00:16:50.970 --> 00:16:53.992 align:middle line:84%
Now if you keep circulating
the same chemicals,

00:16:53.992 --> 00:16:55.450 align:middle line:84%
you're going to
condition your body

00:16:55.450 --> 00:16:58.630 align:middle line:84%
