00:21:47.460 --> 00:21:50.080 align:middle line:84%
great movie-- it sets
this up a little bit more.

00:21:50.080 --> 00:21:52.889 align:middle line:84%
It shows a little
bit more of what

00:21:52.889 --> 00:21:54.180 align:middle line:90%
Dr. Joe was just talking about.

