00:23:25.090 --> 00:23:27.545 align:middle line:90%
How do we break this cycle?

00:23:27.545 --> 00:23:29.780 align:middle line:90%
How does the brain change?

00:23:29.780 --> 00:23:32.110 align:middle line:84%
How does it actually
