>>LISA: So it's a large
part of the brain.

00:24:50.410 --> 00:24:54.290 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: It's what separates
us from most other species.

00:24:54.290 --> 00:24:56.170 align:middle line:90%
It's the CEO of the brain.

