thinking to doing to being.

00:25:11.260 --> 00:25:13.900 align:middle line:84%
Now your thinking brain
is called your neocortex.

00:25:13.900 --> 00:25:16.960 align:middle line:84%
That's that walnut that sits
on the outside with the folds

00:25:16.960 --> 00:25:18.230 align:middle line:90%
and valleys.

00:25:18.230 --> 00:25:21.290 align:middle line:84%
And that is the seat of
your conscious awareness.

00:25:21.290 --> 00:25:23.740 align:middle line:84%
Every time you
learn something new,

00:25:23.740 --> 00:25:25.790 align:middle line:84%
you make a new connection
in your thinking brain.

00:25:25.790 --> 00:25:26.789 align:middle line:90%
That's what learning is.

00:25:26.789 --> 00:25:28.400 align:middle line:90%
Making those connections.

