So you read the book on
how to ride a bicycle,

00:25:30.950 --> 00:25:33.230 align:middle line:84%
you read the book on
how to dance the salsa,

00:25:33.230 --> 00:25:35.450 align:middle line:84%
you read a book on how
to build a doghouse,

00:25:35.450 --> 00:25:38.410 align:middle line:84%
you read a book on success,
how to be a better parent.

00:25:38.410 --> 00:25:41.670 align:middle line:84%
You read a book on
compassion and forgiveness.

00:25:41.670 --> 00:25:44.850 align:middle line:84%
And all of this information is
stored in your thinking brain.

00:25:44.850 --> 00:25:46.330 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: So you make connections.

00:25:46.330 --> 00:25:47.080 align:middle line:90%
>>DISPENZA: Right.

00:25:47.080 --> 00:25:48.360 align:middle line:90%
It's philosophy though.

