It's intellectual data.

00:25:50.970 --> 00:25:52.126 align:middle line:90%
It's facts.

00:25:52.126 --> 00:25:53.750 align:middle line:84%
It's all stored in
your thinking brain.

00:25:53.750 --> 00:25:57.120 align:middle line:84%
Now when you take
that information

00:25:57.120 --> 00:26:00.190 align:middle line:84%
and you apply it, if
