They were already
believing in that outcome

01:01:19.760 --> 01:01:21.770 align:middle line:10%
without any physical
evidence yet.

01:01:21.770 --> 01:01:24.470 align:middle line:10%
>>We are more powerful
than we imagine.

01:01:24.470 --> 01:01:27.030 align:middle line:10%
Within us lies the
key to shifting

01:01:27.030 --> 01:01:30.760 align:middle line:10%
the way life has always
responded and is responding

01:01:30.760 --> 01:01:31.680 align:middle line:10%
to us.

01:01:31.680 --> 01:01:34.700 align:middle line:10%
The only question we
must decide is, are we

01:01:34.700 --> 01:01:37.500 align:middle line:10%
willing to look inward
instead of outward

01:01:37.500 --> 01:01:39.870 align:middle line:10%
and feel the discomfort
and fear that

01:01:39.870 --> 01:01:43.100 align:middle line:10%
comes with changing the
process of our thinking?

01:01:43.100 --> 01:01:46.130 align:middle line:10%
Or in other words, are we
willing to step outside

01:01:46.130 --> 01:01:50.000 align:middle line:10%
of our prison walls and
say yes to the unknown,

01:01:50.000 --> 01:01:51.358 align:middle line:10%
to our adventure?

