>>LISA: All right.

01:01:53.400 --> 01:01:56.940 align:middle line:84%
So how does this relate to
us on a quantum physics level

01:01:56.940 --> 01:01:57.787 align:middle line:90%
exactly?

01:01:57.787 --> 01:01:59.620 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: Well, if
your brain and body are

01:01:59.620 --> 01:02:03.540 align:middle line:84%
