that you can't see or experience

01:02:08.180 --> 01:02:11.090 align:middle line:84%
with your senses yet,
but you've thought

01:02:11.090 --> 01:02:15.130 align:middle line:84%
about enough times in your mind
that your brain is literally

01:02:15.130 --> 01:02:18.544 align:middle line:84%
changed to look like that future
event has already happened?

01:02:18.544 --> 01:02:20.210 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So that's
what visualization is.

01:02:20.210 --> 01:02:21.959 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: You can
call it visualization,

01:02:21.959 --> 01:02:24.247 align:middle line:84%
mental rehearsal, vision
board, whatever it is.

01:02:24.247 --> 01:02:25.080 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: All of that.

01:02:25.080 --> 01:02:27.820 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: But it's not
enough to just think about it

01:02:27.820 --> 01:02:28.650 align:middle line:90%
neurologically.

01:02:28.650 --> 01:02:30.915 align:middle line:84%
Although the brain
will look like,

01:02:30.915 --> 01:02:33.216 align:middle line:84%
from a neuroscience
standpoint, the brain

01:02:33.216 --> 01:02:35.090 align:middle line:84%
will look like it already
had the experience.

01:02:35.090 --> 01:02:36.327 align:middle line:90%
We know that as a fact.

01:02:36.327 --> 01:02:36.910 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

01:02:36.910 --> 01:02:38.451 align:middle line:84%
Well, from what
we've learned so far.

01:02:38.451 --> 01:02:40.194 align:middle line:84%
We do you have to
visually see it?

01:02:40.194 --> 01:02:41.860 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: Well, it
doesn't have to be.

01:02:41.860 --> 01:02:43.830 align:middle line:84%
I don't like to use
the word visualize

01:02:43.830 --> 01:02:45.990 align:middle line:90%
because it omits certain people.

01:02:45.990 --> 01:02:48.400 align:middle line:84%
I like to use the word
mentally rehearse.

01:02:48.400 --> 01:02:51.500 align:middle line:84%
So if I say to a guy sometimes,
can you visualize this?

01:02:51.500 --> 01:02:53.680 align:middle line:84%
Most men will say, I
can't visualize that.

01:02:53.680 --> 01:02:56.946 align:middle line:84%
But if I say, if you
can rehearse mentally,

01:02:56.946 --> 01:02:58.820 align:middle line:84%
can you concept yourself
hitting a golf ball?

01:02:58.820 --> 01:03:00.590 align:middle line:90%
They'll go, oh, absolutely.

01:03:00.590 --> 01:03:02.270 align:middle line:84%
So I like to use
mentally rehearse

01:03:02.270 --> 01:03:06.290 align:middle line:84%
because it's kind of a simpler
way for people to get into it.

01:03:06.290 --> 01:03:08.620 align:middle line:84%
So it's not enough to
just do that though.

01:03:08.620 --> 01:03:14.460 align:middle line:84%
You have to begin to emotionally
embrace that future event

01:03:14.460 --> 01:03:16.900 align:middle line:84%
before it's actually
made manifest.

01:03:16.900 --> 01:03:21.760 align:middle line:84%
So much so that you begin to
convince your body emotionally

01:03:21.760 --> 01:03:24.570 align:middle line:84%
that that future event
has already happened now,

01:03:24.570 --> 01:03:28.510 align:middle line:84%
so much so that you begin to
signal new genes and new ways

01:03:28.510 --> 01:03:31.060 align:middle line:84%
to change your body to look
like the event has happened.

01:03:31.060 --> 01:03:32.640 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So if you
want a new body,

01:03:32.640 --> 01:03:36.150 align:middle line:84%
a different look, you need to
see it, hear it, feel it, taste

01:03:36.150 --> 01:03:36.920 align:middle line:90%
it, smell it.

01:03:36.920 --> 01:03:38.180 align:middle line:90%
You need to integrate it in.

01:03:38.180 --> 01:03:40.680 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: But we don't have
to just say, like, a new body.

01:03:40.680 --> 01:03:41.510 align:middle line:90%
We could say, like--

01:03:41.510 --> 01:03:42.000 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Health.

01:03:42.000 --> 01:03:43.430 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: You
could say wealth.

01:03:43.430 --> 01:03:44.054 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wealth?

01:03:44.054 --> 01:03:44.870 align:middle line:90%
OK, new job.

01:03:44.870 --> 01:03:46.370 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: You
could say a new job.

01:03:46.370 --> 01:03:47.744 align:middle line:84%
You could say a
new relationship.

01:03:47.744 --> 01:03:48.840 align:middle line:90%
You could say joy.

01:03:48.840 --> 01:03:49.760 align:middle line:90%
Here, listen.

01:03:49.760 --> 01:03:52.660 align:middle line:84%
When your brain and body
are physically changed

01:03:52.660 --> 01:03:54.420 align:middle line:84%
to look like the
event has happened,

01:03:54.420 --> 01:03:56.219 align:middle line:84%
then in the quantum
field, the event

01:03:56.219 --> 01:03:58.510 align:middle line:84%
has already happened because
there's physical evidence.

01:03:58.510 --> 01:04:01.190 align:middle line:84%
Now when you get
to this point where

01:04:01.190 --> 01:04:03.790 align:middle line:84%
you're in the state where
you've experienced it

01:04:03.790 --> 01:04:07.190 align:middle line:84%
enough times that you know
that you know, get ready.

01:04:07.190 --> 01:04:09.615 align:middle line:84%
Because the event is
going to find you.

01:04:09.615 --> 01:04:10.490 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It'll happen?

01:04:10.490 --> 01:04:13.084 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: It's going to come
in a way that you least expect.

01:04:13.084 --> 01:04:14.500 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: This is
mental gymnastics.

01:04:14.500 --> 01:04:15.497 align:middle line:90%
This is exciting to me.

01:04:15.497 --> 01:04:16.330 align:middle line:90%
I mean, it's so fun.

01:04:16.330 --> 01:04:17.630 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: It's
going to surprise you.

01:04:17.630 --> 01:04:20.120 align:middle line:84%
It's going to come in a way
that you would never predict.

01:04:20.120 --> 01:04:21.110 align:middle line:90%
And why is that?

01:04:21.110 --> 01:04:23.610 align:middle line:84%
Because if you can predict
it, it's nothing new.

01:04:23.610 --> 01:04:25.300 align:middle line:90%
It's got to be new and unusual.

01:04:25.300 --> 01:04:29.860 align:middle line:84%
And now you have a
two-way relationship

01:04:29.860 --> 01:04:31.710 align:middle line:90%
with this quantum field.

01:04:31.710 --> 01:04:35.810 align:middle line:84%
Because you're not living
in the hormones of survival

01:04:35.810 --> 01:04:37.850 align:middle line:84%
where you're trying to
predict the next moment

01:04:37.850 --> 01:04:39.460 align:middle line:90%
based on the past moment.

01:04:39.460 --> 01:04:42.610 align:middle line:84%
You are trusting in an
outcome beyond your senses.

01:04:42.610 --> 01:04:44.810 align:middle line:84%
And because you're
trusting in the outcome,

01:04:44.810 --> 01:04:47.651 align:middle line:84%
you're in an elevated state and
you feel connected to something

01:04:47.651 --> 01:04:48.150 align:middle line:90%
greater.

01:04:48.150 --> 01:04:50.080 align:middle line:84%
And you would never
try to figure out

01:04:50.080 --> 01:04:52.330 align:middle line:84%
how it's going to happen or
when it's going to happen.

01:04:52.330 --> 01:04:53.680 align:middle line:90%
You're too busy being it.

01:04:53.680 --> 01:04:56.170 align:middle line:84%
The moment you try to figure
out when it's going to happen,

01:04:56.170 --> 01:04:58.470 align:middle line:84%
you've just returned
back to the old self.

01:04:58.470 --> 01:05:02.120 align:middle line:84%
So the beauty here is that when
you change your brain and body

01:05:02.120 --> 01:05:04.330 align:middle line:84%
to look like the event
has already happened,

01:05:04.330 --> 01:05:06.800 align:middle line:84%
they're no longer a
record of the past now.

01:05:06.800 --> 01:05:08.700 align:middle line:90%
Now they're a map to the future.

01:05:08.700 --> 01:05:12.310 align:middle line:84%
And to live by this law is to
live by the quantum law which

01:05:12.310 --> 01:05:15.580 align:middle line:84%
says, environment is an
extension of your mind.

01:05:15.580 --> 01:05:18.300 align:middle line:84%
If you truly change
your mind, there

01:05:18.300 --> 01:05:20.380 align:middle line:90%
should be evidence in your life.

01:05:20.380 --> 01:05:22.060 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Is this how
you healed yourself?

01:05:22.060 --> 01:05:25.102 align:middle line:84%
You had a pretty severe
back injury, didn't you?

01:05:25.102 --> 01:05:25.810 align:middle line:90%
>>DISPENZA: Yeah.

01:05:25.810 --> 01:05:27.790 align:middle line:84%
It kind of started me
on this whole journey.

01:05:27.790 --> 01:05:31.310 align:middle line:90%


01:05:31.310 --> 01:05:34.470 align:middle line:84%
Unfortunately, I think all
of us as human beings usually

01:05:34.470 --> 01:05:38.780 align:middle line:84%
wait for crisis or trauma or
disease or diagnoses or loss.

01:05:38.780 --> 01:05:41.300 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I'm sure you could
explain that neurologically.

01:05:41.300 --> 01:05:45.000 align:middle line:84%
We wait for when the ego
is knocked to its lowest

01:05:45.000 --> 01:05:47.980 align:middle line:84%
denominator before we
get about changing.

01:05:47.980 --> 01:05:50.276 align:middle line:84%
Because when we're
in crisis, we begin

01:05:50.276 --> 01:05:51.400 align:middle line:90%
to examine who we're being.

01:05:51.400 --> 01:05:53.960 align:middle line:84%
We begin to look to see if
these thoughts are loving to us

01:05:53.960 --> 01:05:56.220 align:middle line:84%
or if these behaviors
really support us

01:05:56.220 --> 01:05:58.880 align:middle line:84%
or if these emotions
are really helping

01:05:58.880 --> 01:06:00.800 align:middle line:90%
us to go to a new future.

01:06:00.800 --> 01:06:05.580 align:middle line:84%
So in my situation, I got run
over by a truck in a triathlon

01:06:05.580 --> 01:06:08.950 align:middle line:84%
when I was in my
20s in Palm Springs.

01:06:08.950 --> 01:06:11.950 align:middle line:84%
And I wound up breaking
six bones in my back

01:06:11.950 --> 01:06:14.580 align:middle line:84%
and I had bone fragments
on my spinal cord,

01:06:14.580 --> 01:06:17.740 align:middle line:90%
and was in pretty rough shape.

01:06:17.740 --> 01:06:22.430 align:middle line:84%
And so to make
the story short, I

01:06:22.430 --> 01:06:24.400 align:middle line:84%
had four opinions from
four of the leading

01:06:24.400 --> 01:06:26.080 align:middle line:90%
surgeons in Southern California.

01:06:26.080 --> 01:06:29.470 align:middle line:84%
And they were all recommending
that I had Harrington rod

01:06:29.470 --> 01:06:31.725 align:middle line:84%
surgery, which means
take the back parts off

01:06:31.725 --> 01:06:35.900 align:middle line:84%
of your vertebrae and put in
long, stainless steel rods

01:06:35.900 --> 01:06:39.660 align:middle line:84%
and hopefully that'll get you
back on your feet someday.

01:06:39.660 --> 01:06:42.550 align:middle line:84%
So I decided
against the surgery.

01:06:42.550 --> 01:06:46.540 align:middle line:84%
And I think I was simple enough
and young enough at the time

01:06:46.540 --> 01:06:50.330 align:middle line:84%
to believe that there is some
power that's giving us life.

01:06:50.330 --> 01:06:51.761 align:middle line:90%
Now I wasn't going anywhere now.

01:06:51.761 --> 01:06:52.760 align:middle line:90%
I wasn't doing anything.

01:06:52.760 --> 01:06:55.500 align:middle line:84%
I was lying face down
and I could hardly move.

01:06:55.500 --> 01:06:57.255 align:middle line:90%
And I said, look.

01:06:57.255 --> 01:07:00.160 align:middle line:84%
If I could make contact
with this intelligence

01:07:00.160 --> 01:07:06.960 align:middle line:84%
and begin to give it a
template, a design, something

01:07:06.960 --> 01:07:10.280 align:middle line:84%
that I wanted, and then
surrender it to this mind

01:07:10.280 --> 01:07:12.530 align:middle line:84%
and ask it to resolve it
in a way that was right

01:07:12.530 --> 01:07:15.490 align:middle line:84%
for me, maybe,
just maybe it would

01:07:15.490 --> 01:07:17.070 align:middle line:90%
begin to do the healing for me.

01:07:17.070 --> 01:07:19.960 align:middle line:84%
So I understood
that the power that

01:07:19.960 --> 01:07:22.190 align:middle line:84%
made the body healed
the body, but I think it

01:07:22.190 --> 01:07:25.550 align:middle line:84%
only healed within its
rudimentary, basic way.

01:07:25.550 --> 01:07:27.650 align:middle line:84%
And I was asking it to
go to the next level.

01:07:27.650 --> 01:07:30.860 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Where did you
get that thought at 20?

01:07:30.860 --> 01:07:32.290 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: I was
24 at the time.

01:07:32.290 --> 01:07:37.010 align:middle line:84%
And as I said, you know,
I was a chiropractor.

01:07:37.010 --> 01:07:39.560 align:middle line:84%
And one of the principles
of chiropractic

01:07:39.560 --> 01:07:42.240 align:middle line:84%
is the power that made
the body heals the body.

01:07:42.240 --> 01:07:44.890 align:middle line:84%
And so I made
myself two promises.

01:07:44.890 --> 01:07:47.230 align:middle line:84%
One was that if this
intelligence existed

01:07:47.230 --> 01:07:50.260 align:middle line:84%
and if it was both
personal and universal,

01:07:50.260 --> 01:07:53.280 align:middle line:84%
it was a consciousness, and
consciousness is awareness,

01:07:53.280 --> 01:07:54.790 align:middle line:84%
and awareness is
paying attention.

01:07:54.790 --> 01:07:56.910 align:middle line:84%
So it must be paying
attention to me.

01:07:56.910 --> 01:08:00.360 align:middle line:84%
So I might as well
get really focused

01:08:00.360 --> 01:08:02.550 align:middle line:84%
and get really clear
on what I wanted.

01:08:02.550 --> 01:08:06.700 align:middle line:84%
And so I began to design what
I wanted my spine to look like.

01:08:06.700 --> 01:08:10.030 align:middle line:84%
And if I found my mind
wandering to something else,

01:08:10.030 --> 01:08:12.626 align:middle line:84%
I would stop and
start all over again.

01:08:12.626 --> 01:08:14.000 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So you
trained your mind.

01:08:14.000 --> 01:08:16.416 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: I didn't know that
I was doing it at the time,

01:08:16.416 --> 01:08:19.250 align:middle line:84%
but I began to really
get very focused.

01:08:19.250 --> 01:08:21.500 align:middle line:84%
And then I said that I
won't let any thought go by

01:08:21.500 --> 01:08:22.875 align:middle line:84%
that I didn't want
to experience.

01:08:22.875 --> 01:08:24.721 align:middle line:84%
I just would not
let that happen.

01:08:24.721 --> 01:08:25.470 align:middle line:90%
Like, any thought.

01:08:25.470 --> 01:08:25.979 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What do you mean?

01:08:25.979 --> 01:08:27.978 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: Well, I'm
never going to walk again,

01:08:27.978 --> 01:08:30.779 align:middle line:90%
I'd be paralyzed.

01:08:30.779 --> 01:08:33.260 align:middle line:84%
My friends and family were
telling me to sell my practice.

01:08:33.260 --> 01:08:35.771 align:middle line:90%
And I said, I can't do that.

01:08:35.771 --> 01:08:37.770 align:middle line:84%
And they said, well, it
would be better sell it.

01:08:37.770 --> 01:08:39.228 align:middle line:84%
I said, if I sell
it, then it means

01:08:39.228 --> 01:08:41.380 align:middle line:84%
that I won't be able to
walk, and I can't do that.

01:08:41.380 --> 01:08:44.437 align:middle line:84%
So I just made the
deal with myself

01:08:44.437 --> 01:08:46.020 align:middle line:84%
that I wasn't going
to let any thought

01:08:46.020 --> 01:08:48.479 align:middle line:84%
slip by that I didn't
want to experience.

01:08:48.479 --> 01:08:52.180 align:middle line:84%
So first four weeks
was really torturous,

01:08:52.180 --> 01:08:55.109 align:middle line:84%
because I didn't know
how unfocused I was.

01:08:55.109 --> 01:08:57.470 align:middle line:84%
But after a period
of time I started

01:08:57.470 --> 01:09:00.520 align:middle line:84%
noticing that what I
was doing inside of me

01:09:00.520 --> 01:09:03.080 align:middle line:84%
started to produce some
results outside of me.

01:09:03.080 --> 01:09:05.439 align:middle line:84%
And the moment I noticed
what I did inside

01:09:05.439 --> 01:09:08.950 align:middle line:84%
of me to produce that result
outside of me, I did it again.

01:09:08.950 --> 01:09:11.386 align:middle line:84%
And I began to
heal very quickly.

01:09:11.386 --> 01:09:13.260 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: This was through
the mental rehearsal

01:09:13.260 --> 01:09:14.960 align:middle line:84%
that you were doing,
as you call it.

01:09:14.960 --> 01:09:15.668 align:middle line:90%
>>DISPENZA: Yeah.

01:09:15.668 --> 01:09:19.359 align:middle line:84%
And so I got back on my feet
in about 10 and a half weeks,

01:09:19.359 --> 01:09:22.779 align:middle line:84%
and was back to my normal
life around 11 weeks.

01:09:22.779 --> 01:09:26.700 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I can imagine you became
very impassioned about what

01:09:26.700 --> 01:09:28.405 align:middle line:90%
it means to mentally rehearse.

01:09:28.405 --> 01:09:30.029 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: Well, I
just got very clear

01:09:30.029 --> 01:09:32.810 align:middle line:84%
that mind and body
are very correlated.

01:09:32.810 --> 01:09:34.600 align:middle line:84%
And I just made a
deal with myself

01:09:34.600 --> 01:09:36.819 align:middle line:84%
that I would spend the
rest of my life studying it

01:09:36.819 --> 01:09:38.310 align:middle line:84%
if I was ever able
to walk again.

01:09:38.310 --> 01:09:38.899 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

01:09:38.899 --> 01:09:39.770 align:middle line:90%
That's amazing.

01:09:39.770 --> 01:09:42.290 align:middle line:84%
I hear that from
people in your position

01:09:42.290 --> 01:09:45.490 align:middle line:84%
that have had
incredible careers,

01:09:45.490 --> 01:09:47.423 align:middle line:84%
but it's not even from
your drive or desire

01:09:47.423 --> 01:09:48.214 align:middle line:90%
to have the career.

01:09:48.214 --> 01:09:49.830 align:middle line:84%
It's from that
mission and passion

01:09:49.830 --> 01:09:53.520 align:middle line:84%
that comes from your
experience of healing yourself.

01:09:53.520 --> 01:09:57.590 align:middle line:84%
Have you seen or attracted into
your life-- back to the quantum

01:09:57.590 --> 01:10:01.370 align:middle line:84%
