spontaneous
remissions since then?

01:10:02.787 --> 01:10:05.120 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: You know, that's
been my passion pretty much

01:10:05.120 --> 01:10:06.150 align:middle line:90%
for the last 12 years.

01:10:06.150 --> 01:10:09.890 align:middle line:84%
I've traveled to many different
countries around the world.

01:10:09.890 --> 01:10:12.740 align:middle line:84%
And I studied people
that were diagnosed

01:10:12.740 --> 01:10:15.180 align:middle line:84%
with health conditions,
chronic and acute, whether it

01:10:15.180 --> 01:10:19.620 align:middle line:84%
was cancer, MS, or rheumatoid
arthritis or thyroid

01:10:19.620 --> 01:10:23.030 align:middle line:84%
conditions, our lupus or
chronic pain or depression.

01:10:23.030 --> 01:10:26.437 align:middle line:84%
And they were treating,
you know, conventionally

01:10:26.437 --> 01:10:28.270 align:middle line:84%
or unconventionally,
either getting the same

01:10:28.270 --> 01:10:29.230 align:middle line:90%
or getting worse.

01:10:29.230 --> 01:10:31.310 align:middle line:84%
And all of the sudden,
they got better.

01:10:31.310 --> 01:10:33.880 align:middle line:84%
And so I interviewed
many, many people

01:10:33.880 --> 01:10:37.880 align:middle line:84%
and wanted to find out
what the common things were

01:10:37.880 --> 01:10:42.800 align:middle line:90%
that allowed them to get better.

01:10:42.800 --> 01:10:44.970 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Do you think
by taking a medication

01:10:44.970 --> 01:10:47.904 align:middle line:84%
for a specific disease or
treating that specific disease

01:10:47.904 --> 01:10:50.195 align:middle line:84%
that that's reaffirming that
that disease still exists?

01:10:50.195 --> 01:10:50.820 align:middle line:90%
>>DISPENZA: No.

01:10:50.820 --> 01:10:51.450 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely not.

01:10:51.450 --> 01:10:52.700 align:middle line:90%
I absolutely don't think that.

01:10:52.700 --> 01:10:55.230 align:middle line:84%
I think that you have
three types of stresses:

01:10:55.230 --> 01:10:57.060 align:middle line:84%
physical, chemical,
and emotional.

01:10:57.060 --> 01:11:00.110 align:middle line:84%
Which means you have three types
of ways to create balance back

01:11:00.110 --> 01:11:00.610 align:middle line:90%
in the body.

01:11:00.610 --> 01:11:02.660 align:middle line:84%
Physically, chemically,
and emotionally.

01:11:02.660 --> 01:11:06.800 align:middle line:84%
Now most people will
take the chemical route

01:11:06.800 --> 01:11:09.219 align:middle line:84%
and they'll use
medications, but they're not

01:11:09.219 --> 01:11:10.260 align:middle line:90%
changing their lifestyle.

01:11:10.260 --> 01:11:12.440 align:middle line:84%
They're not doing anything
different physically.

01:11:12.440 --> 01:11:14.500 align:middle line:84%
They're not getting over
their emotional states.

01:11:14.500 --> 01:11:17.730 align:middle line:84%
And so you just can't rely
on just one element of those.

01:11:17.730 --> 01:11:19.420 align:middle line:84%
We have to work on
all three of those.

01:11:19.420 --> 01:11:22.294 align:middle line:84%
So when I study
spontaneous remissions,

01:11:22.294 --> 01:11:24.710 align:middle line:84%
one of the things that I noticed
that people had in common

01:11:24.710 --> 01:11:27.710 align:middle line:84%
is when they were healed,
they knew they were better.

01:11:27.710 --> 01:11:29.390 align:middle line:84%
They didn't have
to take the test.

01:11:29.390 --> 01:11:31.000 align:middle line:90%
They said, I know I'm better.

01:11:31.000 --> 01:11:33.110 align:middle line:84%
And the doctor would
say, how would you know?

01:11:33.110 --> 01:11:35.370 align:middle line:90%
And they say, because I know.

01:11:35.370 --> 01:11:38.800 align:middle line:84%
And of course, they went back
for their tests, their blood

01:11:38.800 --> 01:11:41.660 align:middle line:84%
values, their scans or whatever,
and of course they were better.

01:11:41.660 --> 01:11:44.920 align:middle line:84%
So when you know that you know,
I call that enlightenment.

01:11:44.920 --> 01:11:47.720 align:middle line:84%
Enlightenment is when
you know that you know.

01:11:47.720 --> 01:11:53.110 align:middle line:84%
So it was interesting, because
they had some common things.

01:11:53.110 --> 01:11:55.250 align:middle line:84%
And then my interest
was once I was

01:11:55.250 --> 01:11:58.140 align:middle line:84%
able to demystify that
miraculous healing

01:11:58.140 --> 01:12:00.350 align:middle line:84%
and figure out the
commonalities, the next most

01:12:00.350 --> 01:12:03.580 align:middle line:84%
important thing was,
can I reproduce it?

01:12:03.580 --> 01:12:05.250 align:middle line:84%
So then once I
knew those things,

01:12:05.250 --> 01:12:08.044 align:middle line:84%
then let's see if we can take
people that have conditions

01:12:08.044 --> 01:12:09.460 align:middle line:84%
and let's see if
we can change it.

01:12:09.460 --> 01:12:12.537 align:middle line:84%
And I'm happy to say in the
last two years-- you know,

01:12:12.537 --> 01:12:14.370 align:middle line:84%
and that's why I wrote
"Breaking the Habit."

01:12:14.370 --> 01:12:17.010 align:middle line:84%
Because we've seen
people heal themselves

01:12:17.010 --> 01:12:18.476 align:middle line:90%
of cancer intentionally.

01:12:18.476 --> 01:12:21.740 align:middle line:90%


01:12:21.740 --> 01:12:26.510 align:middle line:84%
Many people from MS, from
lupus, from Hashimoto syndrome,

01:12:26.510 --> 01:12:30.360 align:middle line:84%
from all kinds of
crazy-- diabetes.

01:12:30.360 --> 01:12:32.370 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And once again,
that's by "Breaking

01:12:32.370 --> 01:12:37.400 align:middle line:84%
the Habit of Being Yourself"
is once again reestablishing

01:12:37.400 --> 01:12:39.909 align:middle line:84%
that connection with
the mind and the body,

01:12:39.909 --> 01:12:41.700 align:middle line:84%
and reaffirming and
rehearsing the healing.

01:12:41.700 --> 01:12:41.970 align:middle line:90%
>>DISPENZA: Right.

01:12:41.970 --> 01:12:42.930 align:middle line:90%
And listen.

01:12:42.930 --> 01:12:44.980 align:middle line:84%
Because we can make
thought more real

01:12:44.980 --> 01:12:47.490 align:middle line:84%
than anything else-- that's
the privilege, right?

01:12:47.490 --> 01:12:50.750 align:middle line:84%
So when you begin
to, as an example,

01:12:50.750 --> 01:12:53.600 align:middle line:84%
if you begin to think about
telling your co-worker off

01:12:53.600 --> 01:12:55.845 align:middle line:84%
and you're driving to work
and you're thinking about,

01:12:55.845 --> 01:12:57.970 align:middle line:84%
oh, I'm going to say this
and I'm going to do this.

01:12:57.970 --> 01:12:59.625 align:middle line:84%
No, no, better yet
I'll write an email.

01:12:59.625 --> 01:13:01.622 align:middle line:84%
And you run through the
scenario in your head.

01:13:01.622 --> 01:13:02.830 align:middle line:90%
And then you say, no, no, no.

01:13:02.830 --> 01:13:04.280 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to go to
the boss and then

01:13:04.280 --> 01:13:05.488 align:middle line:90%
we're going to talk about it.

01:13:05.488 --> 01:13:08.262 align:middle line:84%
And you're rehearsing
mentally a new way of being.

01:13:08.262 --> 01:13:10.470 align:middle line:84%
There will come a moment
that the thought that you're

01:13:10.470 --> 01:13:13.800 align:middle line:84%
thinking will literally become
the experience in your brain.

01:13:13.800 --> 01:13:16.700 align:middle line:84%
The moment that
happens, you begin

01:13:16.700 --> 01:13:19.590 align:middle line:84%
to produce the chemistry
as if that future event

01:13:19.590 --> 01:13:20.990 align:middle line:90%
is happening to you now.

01:13:20.990 --> 01:13:24.300 align:middle line:84%
And your body as the unconscious
mind is living in that future

01:13:24.300 --> 01:13:27.660 align:middle line:84%
now, which means your body
literally is physiologically

01:13:27.660 --> 01:13:28.260 align:middle line:90%
changing.

01:13:28.260 --> 01:13:31.490 align:middle line:84%
And by the time you
get to work, you're

01:13:31.490 --> 01:13:33.284 align:middle line:90%
a walking, talking crazy person.

01:13:33.284 --> 01:13:34.700 align:middle line:84%
And all you did
was drive to work.

01:13:34.700 --> 01:13:37.540 align:middle line:84%
We could say that you moved into
a new state of being, right?

01:13:37.540 --> 01:13:42.360 align:middle line:84%
So you and I have been
hypnotized and conditioned

01:13:42.360 --> 01:13:45.120 align:middle line:84%
into believing that we
need a reason for joy,

01:13:45.120 --> 01:13:47.230 align:middle line:84%
that we need a
reason for gratitude.

01:13:47.230 --> 01:13:48.810 align:middle line:90%
That's cause and effect.

01:13:48.810 --> 01:13:51.760 align:middle line:84%
Wait for the experience to
do something before you feel.

01:13:51.760 --> 01:13:53.280 align:middle line:90%
That's very Newtonian physics.

01:13:53.280 --> 01:13:54.400 align:middle line:90%
Very cause and effect.

01:13:54.400 --> 01:13:58.550 align:middle line:84%
I'm saying to give thanks
ahead of the experience.

01:13:58.550 --> 01:14:01.180 align:middle line:84%
So much so that you convince
your body emotionally

01:14:01.180 --> 01:14:02.190 align:middle line:90%
that it's already done.

01:14:02.190 --> 01:14:05.560 align:middle line:84%
Because gratitude means
it's already done.

01:14:05.560 --> 01:14:07.340 align:middle line:84%
You give thanks
when it happened.

01:14:07.340 --> 01:14:09.880 align:middle line:84%
So if your body is
the unconscious mind

01:14:09.880 --> 01:14:13.200 align:middle line:84%
and you can bring up
gratitude ahead of the event,

01:14:13.200 --> 01:14:15.840 align:middle line:84%
then your body begins to believe
that that future event has

01:14:15.840 --> 01:14:17.220 align:middle line:90%
already occurred.

01:14:17.220 --> 01:14:19.780 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So thank you for the
healing that has already begun.

01:14:19.780 --> 01:14:21.279 align:middle line:84%
Thank you for the
money that is in--

01:14:21.279 --> 01:14:23.815 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: But not only
an intellectual process.

01:14:23.815 --> 01:14:25.440 align:middle line:84%
Thoughts are the
language of the brain,

01:14:25.440 --> 01:14:27.190 align:middle line:84%
but feelings are the
language of the body.

01:14:27.190 --> 01:14:29.260 align:middle line:84%
You have to move into
a state of being.

01:14:29.260 --> 01:14:31.940 align:middle line:84%
And so when you can give
thanks and convince your body

01:14:31.940 --> 01:14:34.530 align:middle line:84%
that it's already done, the
environment is no longer

01:14:34.530 --> 01:14:36.030 align:middle line:84%
signaling the gene,
you're signaling

01:14:36.030 --> 01:14:37.446 align:middle line:84%
the gene ahead of
the environment.

01:14:37.446 --> 01:14:39.670 align:middle line:84%
Now it's no longer
cause and effect.

01:14:39.670 --> 01:14:41.500 align:middle line:90%
Now you're causing an effect.

01:14:41.500 --> 01:14:45.860 align:middle line:84%
So when we begin to do that
properly, the beauty behind it

01:14:45.860 --> 01:14:47.920 align:middle line:84%
is then we become
quantum creators.

01:14:47.920 --> 01:14:49.770 align:middle line:84%
So people would say,
oh, that's nonsense.

01:14:49.770 --> 01:14:52.129 align:middle line:84%
And you would say, you're
absolutely correct.

01:14:52.129 --> 01:14:53.670 align:middle line:84%
Quantum physics is
beyond the senses.

01:14:53.670 --> 01:14:55.628 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I am so glad that
you said it that way.

01:14:55.628 --> 01:14:58.520 align:middle line:84%
Because we tend to get very
heady here and speak only

01:14:58.520 --> 01:15:01.260 align:middle line:84%
about the mind and be very
scientific about all of this.

01:15:01.260 --> 01:15:04.990 align:middle line:84%
But your main message is
the connection with the body

01:15:04.990 --> 01:15:07.690 align:middle line:84%
and really, the body's
connection back to the mind,

01:15:07.690 --> 01:15:13.960 align:middle line:84%
and how the body experiences
and expresses what

01:15:13.960 --> 01:15:16.040 align:middle line:90%
it is creating or desiring.

01:15:16.040 --> 01:15:18.990 align:middle line:84%
Now when the chemical reactions
happen through the body,

01:15:18.990 --> 01:15:23.820 align:middle line:84%
does that go beyond the body
also in a vibratory manner?

01:15:23.820 --> 01:15:29.010 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: So we know
from some experiments that

01:15:29.010 --> 01:15:32.850 align:middle line:84%
have been done that if
you take a group of people

01:15:32.850 --> 01:15:37.100 align:middle line:84%
and you set three vials
of DNA in front of them,

01:15:37.100 --> 01:15:39.660 align:middle line:84%
and you say to them, these
are expert players, people

01:15:39.660 --> 01:15:43.200 align:middle line:90%
who really can affect something.

01:15:43.200 --> 01:15:45.540 align:middle line:84%
You say to them, now, with
all of your intention,

01:15:45.540 --> 01:15:49.000 align:middle line:84%
we want you to see this
DNA wind or unwind.

01:15:49.000 --> 01:15:51.930 align:middle line:84%
And you have these people
practice the experiment.

01:15:51.930 --> 01:15:54.940 align:middle line:84%
And you check that DNA at
the end the experiment.

01:15:54.940 --> 01:15:58.770 align:middle line:84%
The power of intention does
absolutely nothing to the DNA.

01:15:58.770 --> 01:16:01.260 align:middle line:84%
Thought does nothing
to change the DNA.

01:16:01.260 --> 01:16:03.260 align:middle line:84%
You say to those
people now, we want

01:16:03.260 --> 01:16:04.750 align:middle line:84%
you to move into
an elevated mood.

01:16:04.750 --> 01:16:07.910 align:middle line:84%
We want you to feel
gratitude or joy or goodwill,

01:16:07.910 --> 01:16:10.210 align:middle line:84%
and we want you to just
emanate this feeling out

01:16:10.210 --> 01:16:13.270 align:middle line:84%
into the quantum field and
do it over and over again.

01:16:13.270 --> 01:16:16.240 align:middle line:84%
If you check the DNA at
the end of that experiment,

01:16:16.240 --> 01:16:18.310 align:middle line:84%
nothing's happened
to the DNA either.

01:16:18.310 --> 01:16:18.994 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Really?

01:16:18.994 --> 01:16:21.160 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: Elevated emotion
did absolutely nothing.

01:16:21.160 --> 01:16:23.650 align:middle line:84%
But when you say to
them, now we want

01:16:23.650 --> 01:16:26.937 align:middle line:84%
you to see the DNA
unwind-- thought.

01:16:26.937 --> 01:16:29.270 align:middle line:84%
And we want you to move into
the elevated emotion of how

01:16:29.270 --> 01:16:32.790 align:middle line:84%
you would feel if
the DNA unwinds.

01:16:32.790 --> 01:16:36.890 align:middle line:84%
25% of the DNA unwinds
at a remote location.

01:16:36.890 --> 01:16:40.250 align:middle line:84%
So our thoughts tend to
be electrical in nature

01:16:40.250 --> 01:16:43.570 align:middle line:84%
and our feelings tend to
be magnetic in nature.

01:16:43.570 --> 01:16:46.320 align:middle line:84%
And how we think
and feel broadcasts

01:16:46.320 --> 01:16:48.360 align:middle line:84%
an electromagnetic
signature that

01:16:48.360 --> 01:16:50.980 align:middle line:84%
influences every single
atom in your life.

01:16:50.980 --> 01:16:53.510 align:middle line:84%
The thought sends a
signal out and the feeling

01:16:53.510 --> 01:16:54.680 align:middle line:90%
draws the event back.

01:16:54.680 --> 01:16:59.700 align:middle line:84%
Now if thinking and feeling
creates a state of being,

01:16:59.700 --> 01:17:02.030 align:middle line:84%
the quantum field responds
to who you're being.

01:17:02.030 --> 01:17:03.630 align:middle line:84%
Not what you think
or what you feel,

01:17:03.630 --> 01:17:05.270 align:middle line:90%
but the combination of them.

01:17:05.270 --> 01:17:08.430 align:middle line:84%
Because that begins to
broadcast the signature.

01:17:08.430 --> 01:17:11.490 align:middle line:84%
So what if you woke
up in the morning

01:17:11.490 --> 01:17:15.830 align:middle line:84%
and you said, what is the
greatest expression of myself

01:17:15.830 --> 01:17:16.940 align:middle line:90%
that I could be today?

01:17:16.940 --> 01:17:19.220 align:middle line:84%
What is the greatest
ideal of myself?

01:17:19.220 --> 01:17:23.560 align:middle line:84%
And let me remind myself how
I'm not going to think today.

01:17:23.560 --> 01:17:27.680 align:middle line:84%
Let me review the thoughts that
bring me back to the old self

01:17:27.680 --> 01:17:29.425 align:middle line:84%
so they would never
slip by unnoticed.

01:17:29.425 --> 01:17:31.550 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Why would you go
to the negative like that?

01:17:31.550 --> 01:17:33.560 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: Because
the importance is

01:17:33.560 --> 01:17:37.990 align:middle line:84%
is to observe them so they
never slip by unnoticed.

01:17:37.990 --> 01:17:39.260 align:middle line:90%
Most people-- think about it.

01:17:39.260 --> 01:17:42.050 align:middle line:84%
Most people, they start
off with good intentions,

01:17:42.050 --> 01:17:44.850 align:middle line:84%
but they wind up on the couch
with the remote control.

01:17:44.850 --> 01:17:46.440 align:middle line:84%
And they just said
two hours earlier

01:17:46.440 --> 01:17:47.606 align:middle line:90%
they were going to work out.

01:17:47.606 --> 01:17:52.360 align:middle line:84%
So you have to begin to denature
the old self neurologically.

01:17:52.360 --> 01:17:53.940 align:middle line:84%
You have to observe
those thoughts,

01:17:53.940 --> 01:17:56.570 align:middle line:84%
observe those behaviors,
observe those emotions,

01:17:56.570 --> 01:17:58.160 align:middle line:84%
so you would never
allow yourself

01:17:58.160 --> 01:17:59.540 align:middle line:90%
to go unconscious to them again.

01:17:59.540 --> 01:18:01.206 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I hadn't
thought of it that way.

01:18:01.206 --> 01:18:05.300 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: The word meditation,
the actual literal translation

01:18:05.300 --> 01:18:07.520 align:middle line:84%
of the word
meditation in Tibetan

01:18:07.520 --> 01:18:10.700 align:middle line:90%
means, to become familiar with.

01:18:10.700 --> 01:18:14.550 align:middle line:84%
So when you become familiar
with your unconscious thoughts,

01:18:14.550 --> 01:18:16.200 align:middle line:84%
when you begin to
notice and become

01:18:16.200 --> 01:18:18.650 align:middle line:84%
familiar with your
unconscious habits,

01:18:18.650 --> 01:18:21.950 align:middle line:84%
and you begin to become familiar
with your unconscious emotions

01:18:21.950 --> 01:18:26.940 align:middle line:84%
and feelings, if you're knowing
yourself, that's meditation.

01:18:26.940 --> 01:18:29.480 align:middle line:84%
Now most people don't want to
light a match in a dark place.

01:18:29.480 --> 01:18:32.520 align:middle line:84%
They'd rather turn on the
TV or get on the computer,

01:18:32.520 --> 01:18:34.470 align:middle line:84%
try to make that
feeling go away.

01:18:34.470 --> 01:18:37.010 align:middle line:84%
The process of
change, first you have

01:18:37.010 --> 01:18:38.900 align:middle line:84%
to become familiar
with the old self

01:18:38.900 --> 01:18:41.230 align:middle line:84%
so much so you're going
into the operating

01:18:41.230 --> 01:18:43.530 align:middle line:84%
system of the subconscious
and bringing it

01:18:43.530 --> 01:18:46.510 align:middle line:84%
to your conscious awareness
so that you know that it would

01:18:46.510 --> 01:18:48.780 align:middle line:90%
never slip by unchecked by you.

01:18:48.780 --> 01:18:53.320 align:middle line:84%
Then if you said, let me remind
myself on who I do want to be.

01:18:53.320 --> 01:18:55.405 align:middle line:84%
And you began to
think in new ways.

01:18:55.405 --> 01:18:57.810 align:middle line:84%
And you began to
plan your behaviors.

01:18:57.810 --> 01:19:00.207 align:middle line:84%
And you became so involved
in that experience

01:19:00.207 --> 01:19:01.790 align:middle line:84%
that the thought
became the experience

01:19:01.790 --> 01:19:04.000 align:middle line:84%
and you began to feel
like that new ideal.

01:19:04.000 --> 01:19:07.930 align:middle line:84%
Now you would get up not as
the same person who sat down.

01:19:07.930 --> 01:19:10.690 align:middle line:84%
Because if you got up as the
same person who sat down,

01:19:10.690 --> 01:19:11.820 align:middle line:90%
nothing's happened.

01:19:11.820 --> 01:19:14.310 align:middle line:84%
In the quantum field,
neurologically, biologically,

01:19:14.310 --> 01:19:15.770 align:middle line:84%
chemically,
genetically, you have

01:19:15.770 --> 01:19:17.240 align:middle line:90%
to get up as somebody else.

01:19:17.240 --> 01:19:19.819 align:middle line:10%
